        {
            "id": 6424462,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲2%，報49550.87點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間17日10:33，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲972.15點（或2%），暫報49550.87點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.82%</li><li>近 1 月：+4.34%</li><li>近 3 月：-1.58%</li><li>近 6 月：+5.72%</li><li>今年以來：+1.07%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以波音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BA-US</a>)領漲。波音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BA-US</a>)上漲5.05%；宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)上漲4.63%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)上漲4.32%；3M(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MMM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MMM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MMM-US</a>)上漲3.69%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXP-US</a>)上漲3.29%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)下跌4.71%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)下跌0.5%；沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)下跌0.12%；嬌生(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JNJ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JNJ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JNJ-US</a>)下跌0.03%。</p></section></main>",
